  },
  {
    index: 2,
    title: "Contract & Development Kickoff",
    description: "Once you approve the proposal, we'll set up a flexible monthly payment plan and begin development immediately. Our Laravel experts will design the system architecture, create database schemas, and establish API structures. Development follows an agile methodology with regular demos and feedback sessions to ensure we're building exactly what you need."
  },
  {
    index: 3,
    title: "Delivery & Ongoing Support",
    description: "After thorough testing and your approval, we deploy your Laravel application to your preferred hosting environment. Our relationship doesn't end at launchâ€”we provide ongoing maintenance and support on a monthly basis, handling updates, performance optimization, security patches, and new feature implementation as your business grows."
